fields.System.Description:
RTC Test Case Description:
At the customer level, the system must have a field on the customer amend screen named "Last Customer Transaction Source", it must capture the system that updated the "Last Customer Transaction date" field. Success Criteria: At the customer level, system has a field on the customer amend screen named "Last Customer Transaction Source", it captured the system that updated the "Last Customer Transaction date" field.
